screen_desc: The screenshot displays a Telegram app interface with options related to account management. It includes features such as "Add another account," "Set a Passcode," "Clear Cache," "Change Phone Number," and "Contact Support." At the bottom, there is a prominent "Log Out" button, accompanied by a note indicating that logging out will deactivate all Secret Chats. The layout is clean, with icons next to each option for easy identification.
